---@param velocity_x number The x component of the base start velocity of the particle
---@param velocity_y number The y component of the base start velocity of the particle
---@param velocity_z number The z component of the base start velocity of the particle
---@param size_x number The x component of the start size of the particle (width)
---@param size_y number The y component of the start size of the particle (height)
---@param size_z number The z component of the start size of the particle (breadth)
---@param size_end number The size multiplier. The particles size at the end of it's lifetime will be it's start size multiplied by this value
---@param start_color_r integer The r (red) component of the start color of the particle
---@param start_color_g integer The g (green) component of the start color of the particle
---@param start_color_b integer The b (blue) component of the start color of the particle
---@param start_color_a integer The a (alpha) component of the start color of the particle
---@param gravity number The (vertical) gravity applied to the particle
---@param rotation number The rotation applied to the particle. Rotation is only applied to the Y axis and it is specified in radians per second
---@param velocity_var_x number The x component of the start velocity variance of the particle
---@param velocity_var_y number The y component of the start velocity variance of the particle
---@param velocity_var_z number The z component of the start velocity variance of the particle
---@param end_color_r integer The r (red) component of the end color of the particle
---@param end_color_g integer The g (green) component of the end color of the particle
---@param end_color_b integer The b (blue) component of the end color of the particle
